OL,6,FA woman who stabbed her former partner
OL,7,Fto death with a kitchen knife after an
OL,8,Fargument has been jailed for life.
OL,10,FStephanie McLaggan and Gillian
OL,11,FConnelly, who had been together for
OL,12,Fmore than 20 years, were at the home
OL,13,Fof their friend Jade Glover in
OL,14,FGainsborough, Lincolnshire, when a row
OL,15,Fbroke out in the early hours of 28
OL,16,FJuly last year.
OL,18,FMcLaggan, 39, took a knife from the
OL,19,Fkitchen and stabbed 44-year-old Ms
OL,20,FConnelly in the chest.
