OL,6,FAfter the stabbing, Glover and another
OL,7,Ffriend, Steven Lowther, helped
OL,8,FMcLaggan move the body into the street
OL,9,Fin an attempt to cover up the crime.
OL,11,FMcLaggan was arrested less than 24
OL,12,Fhours later. She denied murder but was
OL,13,Fconvicted after a trial.
OL,15,FShe was jailed for a minimum of 18
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FGlover, 28, and Lowther, 45, both of
OL,19,FWheeldon Street, pleaded guilty to
OL,20,Fperverting the course of justice and
OL,21,Fwill be sentenced at a later date.
